At UNC, we have an institution-wide page for forgotten passwords, and we'd like it if the login instructions were specific to our logins.  There has been confusion among users logging into confluence about which UID they need to use, and about where to go about forgotten passwords.  I've edited login.vm to reflect our setup, but I'll have to change it again next time I upgrade confluence.  This page should be one of the admin-customizable templates in the UI so that these kind of things get remembered between versions.

